title: Minor girl raped, stabbed to death in Palwal; accused held
content: A five-year-old girl was kidnapped, brutally raped and stabbed to death allegedly by a man who used to work at her father's tent house in Asaoti village in Haryana's Palwal district.     Previous Article    Transgenders : ‘Caricaturing on screen have enforced stereotype..
